{"tid":2452572,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港台：：北韓官媒點名BTS　抨擊南韓培訓方式","createTime":"2021-03-19T02:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:25:17.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d31cc864e244d0352c8e11ccdbba55111bf0d0e3","tid":2452572,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓的K-pop組合近年越來越受歡迎，例如BTS防彈少年團，早前更加在格林美頒獎禮上表演，引起不少樂迷的關注。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<strong>作為鄰居的北韓</strong>，似乎就不希望K-pop文化入侵社會，有北韓傳媒近日抨擊南韓培訓明星的方式，令青少年過著悲慘的生活，被認為是試圖令北韓民眾厭惡南韓文化的舉措。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581424-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581424-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=bab96238\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581424-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=586376e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581424-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"54d526cc2fc9dd7a4863e58590543124b7aab062","tid":2452572,"uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"夠北韓一般民眾悽慘？<br />\n不過呢啲野對身處鳥籠下嘅北韓人民來說係唔會明白。"},{"pid":"2718d90e23a160189058dbcfb82e9f10a271fcd4","tid":2452572,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"金仔心聲：屌你培訓男團我J乜撚？"},{"pid":"d46a522932be5067ea940e0040bbd8d75e576b36","tid":2452572,"uid":217565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2718d90e23a160189058dbcfb82e9f10a271fcd4","tid":2452572,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"金仔心聲：屌你培訓男團我J乜撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"好似話埋bp<img src=\"/assets/faces/do